<seg id="b.ACT.20.35" type="verse">Alle I haue schewed vnto ȝowe, 13þat þoo þat þus traueylen hit bihoues to receyue þo infirme (or, þo febul), ande alsso forto þenke on13 þo worde of oure Lorde Iesu, þo whiche he saide, þat hit es more blessed to gife þanne forto take.
<seg id="b.ACT.20.36" type="verse">Ande whanne he hade saide alle þise, he kneled ande preyed wiþ hem alle.
