<seg id="b.ACT.21.11" type="verse">He, whanne he come vnto vs, he toke þo girdel of Poule, ande bonde Poules hende ande hise fete, ande saide, Þis sais þo Holygoste, Þus schal þo Iewes þat ben in Ierusalem bynde þo man þat owes þis girdel, ande þei schal bitake hym into þe hende of nacyons.
<seg id="b.ACT.21.12" type="verse">Ande whanne we harde þis, we ande þoo þat wore of þat place preyde hym þat he schulde noghte go vnto Ierusalem.
